HEADWORD: Arenga
<hw>A*ren"ga</hw></mhw>
<pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Malayan.]</ety> <def>A palm tree
(<spn>Saguerus saccharifer</spn>) which furnishes sago, wine, and fibers
for ropes; the gomuti palm.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

